{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would tell me a couple of days, if I would-- tell-- if I could tell in the minutest detail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just that something was all the time happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And throughout this all, it was those-- this-- those-- those-- we had-- By that stage, we had a lot of female guards.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were vicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were atrocious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were just-- you know, it was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, there was no-- if the men-- if the men had no-- if the men were-- didn't have any compassion or didn't have, you know, any-- but the girls were even worse.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they were just absolutely, you know, like-- woo!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To sort of-- to, to sort of-- you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To really to devastate you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To totally finish you off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To sort of know-- You didn't register.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were just nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were just absolutely nothing to them, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To the men and to the women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it manifested itself-- perhaps because I was a girl, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it did-- it was-- And yet, throughout this all, what sustained us-- obviously, this would not have sustained us-- it-- what sustained us, it was the, the-- those seven girls, in particular.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- this was already bonded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is, you know, even a sort of-- behind the back, you know-- a way for even, you know, [INAUDIBLE] or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we really couldn't talk to one another during the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could not talk to one another during the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But occasionally, as I said, we took a chance and we stole a glance or we-- you know, after all, you had eyes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Occasionally you felt that it is-- you know, that you-- but you-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
